label: context
comment: This is a vocabulary document and is used to achieve certain features of the JSON-LD language.

label: expanded
comment: This link relation is used to reference a JSON-LD context from a JSON document so that it can be interpreted as JSON-LD.

label: compacted
comment: This profile URI is used to request or specify expanded JSON-LD document form.

label: flattened
comment: This profile URI is used to request or specify flattened JSON-LD document form.
